                    <div style="flex:4;" class="text-muted text-justify f-18">
                        <p>BPS is steeped in more than 40 years of rich history and tradition that began with the extraordinary vision of one man — Late Shri S. L. Batra. From teaching classes in the 1980s in a tiny shed to securing acres of land in East Delhi,
                            Shri S.L. Batra was a true educationist. He long envisioned a progressive school that offered education as an experience to anyone eager to learn and willing to work hard. Inspired by a deep love of learning, the gifts of nature and
                            the diversity of humanity, Late Shri S. L. Batra set out to bring a better educational experience at a time and place where it was needed most.</p>
                        <p>
    
                    </div>
                    <div style="flex:3;" class="text-center mx-0 ml-md-4 mb-3">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="Richhistory/1.JPG" alt="">
    
                    </div>
    
                </div>
            </div>
    
            <div class="row my-4">
