                    <img class="w-100" src="Richhistory/2.jpg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 text-muted text-justify">
                    <p class=" f-18">
                        Bharti Public School, Swasthya Vihar has been blossoming with a spirit and a vision to ignite the passion for learning among its students, for the past four decades. Ever since the inception of the school it has made rapid strides & phenomenal progress
                        and has won itself a niche among the leading schools of East Delhi. The journey from aspiration to achievement has been a long one. The edifice ‘Unfolding the Infinite Potential’ stands true under the tutelage and direction of the
                        current Principal, Dr. Savita Arora, a recipient of the National Teacher’s Award awarded by the Hon’ble President of India, Dr. Pranab Mukherjee.
    
                    </p>
    
                </div>
    
            </div>
            <div class="my-5">

                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row">
                    <div style="flex:4;" class="text-justify text-muted f-18">
                       
                        <p>
                            BPS is a proud recipient of the British Council’s International School Award for the second time in row and as a part of the same; the school pursues regular national and international exchange programmes with the U.K., USA and France for teachers and
                            students, thereby developing global perspective and cementing lifelong relationships.</p>
                            <p> The green school campus boasts of an excellent infrastructure with modern facilities like smart boards. The well stocked digital library provides the latest & up-to-date books for reading & reference material. It has fully equipped computer and science
                                labs with updated internet facilities.</p>
    
                    </div>
                    <div style="flex:3;" class="text-center mx-0 ml-md-4 mb-3">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="Richhistory/3.jpg" alt="">
    
                    </div>
    
                </div>
                <div class="text-muted">
                    <p>
                        The school auditorium & an amphitheatre provides a conducive environment for holding various events in the school. It is an excellent arena for budding sports persons with facilities for indoor
                        and outdoor games. The school boasts of full-fledged cricket, skating, badminton & basketball academies being run by ex-international players. Many of our sports stars have participated and won accolades at the National School Games.
                       </p>
                </div>

            </div>
    
            <div class="row my-4">
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-2">
                    <img class="w-100" src="Richhistory/OK_2004.jpg" alt="">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <p class="text-muted text-justify f-18">
                        Growth happens outside the comfort zone. Your Upper School experience will challenge you to
                        break through your comfort zone — whether that’s trying new sports, creative arts or community
                        outreach program, opportunities to discover your untapped talents and passions await around
                        every corner. Your self-discovery is supported by the entire BPS community to prepare you for
                        the real world.
    
    
    
    
                    </p>
    
                </div>
    
            </div>
